    {
      "id": "PopularPost355727",
      "post_content": "I'll say it again and again for people who like to hate \"punisher\" cards and trot out the \"Your opponent will always pick what's better for them!\" line:  \n  \nYour opponent won't always KNOW what's better for them. They (usually) don't know exactly what's in your hand, in the rest of your library, and (most importantly) what you've got planned for them in your head.  \n  \nAlso, lots of players (even the sharpest cats in competitive play) will sometimes make an irrational choice.  \n  \nYES, you \\*DO\\* need to build around a punisher strategy a bit.  \n  \nYES, [Blazing Salvo](/Pages/Card/Details.aspx?name=Blazing Salvo) is not an auto 4-of in every burn deck.  \n  \nI really hope this gets reprinted in some set that will be legal in modern.",
      "posted_by": "Paleopaladin",
      "html": "<div class=\"post oddItem\" id=\"PopularPost355727\">\n<span class=\"postContent\" id=\"ctl00_ctl00_ctl00_MainContent_SubContent_SubContent_popularPosts_postsRepeater_ctl07_post\">I'll say it again and again for people who like to hate \"punisher\" cards and trot out the \"Your opponent will always pick what's better for them!\" line:<br/><br/>Your opponent won't always KNOW what's better for them.  They (usually) don't know exactly what's in your hand, in the rest of your library, and (most importantly) what you've got planned for them in your head.<br/><br/>Also, lots of players (even the sharpest cats in competitive play) will sometimes make an irrational choice.<br/><br/>YES, you *DO* need to build around a punisher strategy a bit.<br/><br/>YES, <a class=\"autoCard\" data:cardname=\"Blazing Salvo\" href=\"/Pages/Card/Details.aspx?name=Blazing Salvo\">Blazing Salvo</a> is not an auto 4-of in every burn deck.<br/><br/>I really hope this gets reprinted in some set that will be legal in modern.</span>\n<div class=\"postDetails\" id=\"ctl00_ctl00_ctl00_MainContent_SubContent_SubContent_popularPosts_postsRepeater_ctl07_postDetails\" style=\"padding-top: 5px;\">\n<div class=\"reportAbuse\">\n<a href=\"http://wizards.custhelp.com/cgi-bin/wizards.cfg/php/enduser/ask.php?p_prods=522,706,739&amp;p_cats=\" id=\"ctl00_ctl00_ctl00_MainContent_SubContent_SubContent_popularPosts_postsRepeater_ctl07_reportAbuseLink\" onclick=\"HandleReportPost(this, '355727'); return false;\">\r\n                                    Report Abuse</a>\u00a0\u00a0\r\n                                \r\n                            </div>\n<div class=\"postedBy\">\r\n                                Posted By: \r\n                                <span id=\"PostedBy31075\">Paleopaladin</span>\r\n                                (12/26/2013 6:27:39 PM)\r\n                            </div>\n<div class=\"postRating\">\n<div class=\"postRatingLabel\">\r\n                                    Ra